{"tid":1540073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[急問]林鄭今日六點個live 頭髮仲長過厚過琴日？","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:48:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:57:37.000Z","uid":271477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"13879e3ab4022eae0b4c308955356b0e5179de9f","tid":1540073,"uid":271477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:48:01.000Z","msg":"請問係咪我錯覺？佢今日六點個live, 頭髮仲長過琴日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jN3qr8M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjN3qr8M.jpg&h=c5e9f5e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖係今日六點live, 下圖係琴日見記者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就當琴日梳高左，但個厚度都幾明顯厚過琴日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前面pat 小小陰如是，都長過琴日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係今日live, 又會咁既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生髮速度神速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢之前流出段野講話剪唔到頭髮，咁即係呢段野一早錄定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵人幫手排下個時間序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n若是我自膠，請不推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對唔住我係P牌仔，但真係真心問"},{"pid":"ebaa51f01896ad6e3622299580319b21e856ce3c","tid":1540073,"uid":271477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:48:50.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"e67d6942e8d7837ae9fb8b884c02be3449f07166","tid":1540073,"uid":271477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:49:04.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"f8d6d8d9c52ba35412a98c7484287ab90792d66a","tid":1540073,"uid":2714